md paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="ml mm go mn bg mo"><div class="mc md me"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*STEaGieHD_rEaU6P4CFyqQ.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="" class="bg mp mq c" width="700" height="408" loading="eager" role="presentation"/></picture></div></div><figcaption class="mr ms mt mc md mu mv be b bf z hb">Star Atlas Guilds Homepage</figcaption></figure><h1 id="a37a" class="mw mx ev be my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt bj">Star Atlas Guilds Shutting Down</h1><p id="386f" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le nu lg lh li nv lk ll lm nw lo lp lq nx ls lt lu ny lw lx ly eo bj">The original and popular Star Atlas Guilds website is shutting down, an inadvertent result of the new Star Atlas Intellectual Property policy. The rollout of the Star Atlas IP policy is intended to open up opportunities to the Star Atlas community to develop with and around the Star Atlas intellectual property framework.</p><p id="9312" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le lf lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq lr ls lt lu lv lw lx ly eo bj">However, a stipulation of the policy is that the words “Star” and “Atlas” cannot be used conjunctively in a project’s name, including it’s website domain address.</p><p id="41f7" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le lf lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq lr ls lt lu lv lw lx ly eo bj">Hence, the problem for Star Atlas Guilds lies in both its namesake and web address.</p><p id="369e" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le lf lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq lr ls lt lu lv lw lx ly eo bj">Upon further inquiry by Hologram News, it was determined that Star Atlas Guilds was directed to change its name to conform with Star Atlas IP policy or to cease operations.</p><p id="ef48" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le lf lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq lr ls lt lu lv lw lx ly eo bj">Star Atlas Guilds is managed and run by Star Atlas community member Dodger. In our brief discussion with Dodger, they mentioned that currently there are no plans to either change the service’s name or transfer management to another party.</p><h1 id="ec05" class="mw mx ev be my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt bj">A Focal Point of Guilds</h1><p id="ea25" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le nu lg lh li nv lk ll lm nw lo lp lq nx ls lt lu ny lw lx ly eo bj">Star Atlas Guilds is a popular website used by Star Atlas players to search, learn, and connect with the many Star Atlas guilds. Star Atlas Guilds has been serving the community for a significant period of time. Its closure will leave a service capability gap in the community until a similar service is provided.</p><p id="8087" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le lf lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq lr ls lt lu lv lw lx ly eo bj">On the website, players can search for guilds based on a number of criteria including faction allegiance and gameplay activity. Each guild description provided substantial information about a guild along with multiple points of contact.</p><p id="24de" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le lf lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq lr ls lt lu lv lw lx ly eo bj">It is unknown if there are plans to preserve the valuable content contained within the website.</p></div></div></div><div class="ab ca nz oa ob oc" role="separator"><span class="od bx bl oe of og"></span><span class="od bx bl oe of og"></span><span class="od bx bl oe of"></span></div><div class="eo ep eq er es"><div class="ab ca"><div class="ch bg dx dy dz ea"><h1 id="75cb" class="mw mx ev be my mz oh nb nc nd oi nf ng nh oj nj nk nl ok nn no np ol nr ns nt bj">About the Author</h1><p id="add5" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le nu lg lh li nv lk ll lm nw lo lp lq nx ls lt lu ny lw lx ly eo bj"><a class="af mb" href="https://medium.com/u/41e0c5b141f1?source=post_page-----4922901fb224--------------------------------" rel="noopener">Krigs</a> is a pioneer in the world of Star Atlas, having founded The Hologram News Network — an independent meta-news organization that keeps players up to date on all developments regarding Star Atlas. An ardent supporter of emerging technologies, Krigs has been covering this game for over a year and believes passionately in their power to revolutionize our collective gaming experience.</p><p id="73ec" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le lf lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq lr ls lt lu lv lw lx ly eo bj">Follow on Social Media:</p><p id="3b31" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le lf lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq lr ls lt lu lv lw lx ly eo bj"><a class="af mb" href="https://open.spotify.com/show/2mxndrDW6yPfpS350ijzjt?si=ec7c717f998240d6" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Podcast</a> | <a class="af mb" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDa-YxgNG6A9xpH1qyP0OaQ" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">YouTube</a> | <a class="af mb" href="https://twitter.com/home" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Twitter</a> | <a class="af mb" href="https://twitter.com/home" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Instagram</a> | <a class="af mb" href="https://thehologram.io/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Web</a></p><h1 id="d886" class="mw mx ev be my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt bj">About The Hologram</h1><p id="bd30" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le nu lg lh li nv lk ll lm nw lo lp lq nx ls lt lu ny lw lx ly eo bj"><a class="af mb" href="https://medium.com/the-hologram" rel="noopener">The Hologram</a> is Star Atlas’ first and only independent news network. Our vision is to become the most trusted source of information about Star Atlas and a voice for the whole community. Readers can expect a high standard from our reporting and staff. Our promise to you: we will not publish anything that hasn’t been thoroughly researched and based on the best facts available.</p><p id="503c" class="pw-post-body-paragraph lb lc ev ld b le lf lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq lr ls lt lu lv lw lx ly eo bj">The Hologram is not endorsed by the <a class="af mb" href="https://staratlas.com/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Star Atlas</a> team. Any information published by The Hologram or its writers should be considered as informational in nature and does not constitute any financial advice.</p></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></article><div class="ab ca"><div class="ch bg dx dy dz ea"></div></div></div><div class="ab ca"><div class="ch bg dx dy dz ea"><div class="om on ab hk"><div class="oo ab"><a class="op ax am ao" rel="noopener follow" href="/tag/star-atlas?source=post_page-----e4da1d94be33---------------star_atlas-----------------"><div class="oq go cw or os ot ou be b bf z bj ov">Star Atlas</div></a></div><div class="oo ab"><a class="op ax am ao" rel="noopener follow" href="/tag/community?source=post_page-----e4da1d94be33---------------community-----------------"><div class="oq go cw or os ot ou be b bf z bj ov">Community</div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="l"></div><footer class="ow ox oy oz pa pb pc pd pe ab q pf gs c"><div class="l ae"><div class="ab ca"><div class="ch bg dx dy dz ea"><div class="ab co pg"><div class="ab q jh"><div class="ph l"><span class="l pi pj pk e d"><div class="ab q jh"><div class="pw-multi-vote-icon go ho ji jj jk"><div class=""><div class="jl jm jn jo jp jq jr am js jt ju jk"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-label="clap"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M11.37.83L12 3.28l.63-2.45h-1.26zM15.42 1.84l-1.18-.39-.34 2.5 1.52-2.1zM9.76 1.45l-1.19.4 1.53 2.1-.34-2.5zM20.25 11.84l-2.5-4.4a1.42 1.42 0 0 0-.93-.64.96.96 0 0 0-.75.18c-.25.19-.4.42-.45.7l.05.05 2.35 4.13c1.62 2.95 1.1 5.78-1.52 8.4l-.46.41c1-.13 1.93-.